  50,36,"Acêal isuta ay Nesqucc uqbel nnsen! Llan $elben ten di loehd. Qelben, di tmurt, anda t ssôan"
  50,37,"Deg waya, s tidep, asmekti i win isâan ul, ne$ ifkan tameééu$t, u d anagi"
  50,38,"Ni$ Nxelq ed tamurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, di sdis wussan, ur Naâyi"
